&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1136%2Fjech.56.5.322&amp;rft.aulast=Knottnerus&amp;rft.aufirst=J+A&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAlvan+Feinstein\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Yach-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-Yach_9-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-Yach_9-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Yach, Derek; Bialous, Stella Aguinaga (2001). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC1446867\">\"Junking Science to Promote Tobacco\"</a>. <i>American Journal of Public Health</i>. <b>91</b> (11): 1745\u20131748. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.2105/AJPH.91.11.1745\">10.2105/AJPH.91.11.1745</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/PubMed_Central\" title=\"PubMed Central\">PMC</a>&#160;<span class=\"plainlinks\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC1446867\">1446867</a>&#8239;<img alt=\"Freely accessible\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/65/Lock-green.svg/9px-Lock-green.svg.png\" title=\"Freely accessible\" width=\"9\" height=\"14\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/65/Lock-green.svg/14px-Lock-green.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/65/Lock-green.svg/18px-Lock-green.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"512\" data-file-height=\"813\" /></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=American+Journal+of+Public+Health&amp;rft.atitle=Junking+Science+to+Promote+Tobacco&amp;rft.volume=91&amp;rft.issue=11&amp;rft.pages=1745-1748&amp;rft.date=2001&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC1446867&amp;rft_id=inf